                    <span>Shadow Divers gives a different perspective to Chowdhury's "The Last Dive".  This is also a must-read if you are a diver on the east coast.  The personal stories of the two overly dedicated men that gave everything for a WWII wreck makes for an unbelievable read.  Great book.</span>
                  
